<headline>Heat Advisory issued July 15 at 10:58AM CDT until July 15 at 9:00PM CDT by NWS Amarillo</headline>
<description>...HEAT ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 PM CDT THIS EVENING...
* WHAT...High temperatures around 105 expected
* WHERE...In Oklahoma, Texas County. In Texas, Hansford, Hutchinson,
Moore and Sherman Counties.
* WHEN...Until 9 PM CDT this evening.
* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures may cause heat illnesses.</description>
<instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.
Take extra precautions when outside. Wear lightweight and loose
fitting clothing. Try to limit strenuous activities until the
evening. Take action when you see symptoms of heat exhaustion and
heat stroke.</instruction>
